I prefer that evil people not have access to weapons of mass destruction.  As much as everyone rails against Bush, he's not an evil man.  Hussein most assuredly is.  Would you feel comfortable if Hussein had the destructive power of the USA at his beck and call?  You may not feel comfortable with Bush in that position, but be honest...   Who would you fear more in that position?<br>
